oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Leon McAuliffe and his Western Swing Band - December 1947 session - M5, M6
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: "Don't Be Blue" (master #5) and "Sittin' On Top Of The World" (master #6) performed by Leon McAuliffe and his Western Swing Band from their December 1947 recording session. These takes were later dubbed and compiled onto another disc (see TR001646_1).
